    "biography": "<p>A giant Awakened wolf spider (Lycosa saltator) whose venom sets victims dancing uncontrollably. Kept, improbably, as a pet.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> Enhanced Senses (Thermographic Vision), Venom</p><p><em>Attacks: Venom bite, [Essence]M, Reach −1. Habitat: Wide range of damp land terrains. Range: Most of southern Europe. Venom secondary effect: Body Test (TN = the spider's Essence); failure makes the victim jerky and uncoordinated for [Essence]D6 turns (a 'dancing spell'), repeating until they score 1+ successes on the Body Test at its end. Each dancing spell deals 6L Stun. Book Strength 0, Intelligence 1/3. PAE p.103.</em></p>",
